data.description: Made in the shade of giant oaks sits this beautiful Acadian 3br 2ba 2083 heating and cooled square foot home that offers large family room with 10'ceiliings, wet bar, butlers' kitchen with marble island that is just perfect for the baker in the family, custom cabinets, private dining room, large bedrooms, master suite with claw tub, glassed in 10x64 glassed in porch and more. This beautiful home sits on 5.22 acres and also has a 3br 1ba mother-in-law 1138 sq/ft apartment, 16x24 workshop, 12x24 shed, and more.  It is worth the view. 2023-09-08
